# CampusConnect — Project Analysis

## Overview

**CampusConnect** is a full-stack campus management platform for IUT-Dhaka students. It provides a central hub for campus social/administrative activities with a maroon-and-white university theme.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | React 19, Vite, Tailwind CSS v3, DaisyUI, React Router v7, Lucide React, React Hot Toast, Axios, Firebase SDK |
| **Backend** | Node.js, Express 4, Firebase Admin SDK (auth) |
| **Primary DB** | PostgreSQL via **Prisma ORM** (user accounts & relational data) |
| **Secondary DB** | MongoDB via **Mongoose** (all feature/activity data) |
| **Auth** | Google Firebase Auth → custom JWT (signed with string `'Blink'`) |
| **Background Jobs** | `node-cron` (cleanup job) |
| **Emails** | `nodemailer` |

---

## Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    FE["Frontend\nReact/Vite :5173"]
    BE["Backend\nExpress :4000"]
    PG["PostgreSQL\n(Prisma ORM)\nUsers, LostItem, BloodRequest\nDonorRecord, RoommateListing"]
    MG["MongoDB\n(Mongoose)\nSociety, Event, Feedback\nMarketplacePost, Notification, NotificationRead"]
    FB["Firebase\n(Google OAuth)"]

    FE -- "REST API + JWT Bearer" --> BE
    BE -- "Prisma Client" --> PG
    BE -- "Mongoose" --> MG
    FE -- "Google Sign-In" --> FB
    FB -- "ID Token" --> BE
    BE -- "JWT Response" --> FE
```

